Package org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.util.gson

Class UnitFieldAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gson.TypeAdapter<Double>
      • org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.util.gson.UnitFieldAdapter
  • public class UnitFieldAdapter
extends com.google.gson.TypeAdapter<Double>
    Adapter for JSON fields which translates values as string representatives to actual double values, e.g.
    for distances: "10 km" -> 10000, "10 cm" -> 0.1, "0.5m" -> 0.5
    for speeds: "10 km/h" -> 2.77, "10 m/s" -> 10, "35 mph" -> 15.6464

    Usage: 
    
  @JsonAdapter(UnitFieldAdapter.DistanceMeters.class)
  public double distance;
